---
By: John of the Cross
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 334
    Verse: 7
Tags:
  - Nothing
---
That you may have pleasure in everything, seek pleasure in nothing. That
you may know everything, seek to know nothing. That you may possess all
things, seek to possess nothing. That you may be everything, seek to be
nothing.
